---
---
<section class="py-20 bg-slate-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
  {/* Abstract Background Elements for Dark Section */}
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-20">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-sky-500 rounded-full blur-[120px] mix-blend-screen transform translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/4"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-[#77BA55] rounded-full blur-[100px] mix-blend-screen transform -translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-6">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#77BA55]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
        </svg>
        Learner Experience
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">The Funnel Does Not End at Checkout</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300">
        A strong course funnel continues after purchase. Students should know how to log in, where to start, what to complete first, where to find resources, and how to get support.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
      {[
        'Purchase confirmation',
        'Login instructions',
        'Course access email',
        'Welcome lesson',
        'First-week guidance',
        'Resource instructions',
        'Student FAQ',
        'Support pathway',
        'Progress reminders',
        'Completion encouragement'
      ].map(item => (
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-3 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
             <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white/80" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white/90">{item}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto backdrop-blur-sm">
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 font-medium leading-relaxed">
        This makes TheEduAssist different from basic funnel builders. <span class="text-white">We connect marketing automation with the learner experience.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
